content.warning: Sezvo iyi application inoshanda kune yakakura nhamba yemvumo pafoni yako mbozha, Mvumo zhinji dzine njodzi zvakanyanya, saka usatore kana kuvauraya pasina kunyatsoziva njodzi dzemusika kana script.
